# Paisley Photography Portfolio

Static photography portfolio built with Astro 5 + Tailwind CSS 4, hosted on Cloudflare Pages.

## Architecture

- **Site:** Astro static site in `src/` ‚Üí deployed to Cloudflare Pages (auto-deploys on push to `main`)
- **Contact form Worker:** `worker/index.js` ‚Üí deployed separately via `wrangler deploy` from the `worker/` directory
- **Portfolio API Worker:** `worker/portfolio/index.js` ‚Üí manages portfolio images in R2, serves admin UI at `/admin`
- **Domain:** `paisleys.work`

## Portfolio Image Management

Images are stored in Cloudflare R2 and managed via a dedicated Worker with a browser-based admin panel.

- **Admin UI:** `https://<portfolio-worker-url>/admin` ‚Äî upload, delete, reorder, edit alt text
- **Public API:** `GET /api/images` returns the image list; `GET /images/:key` serves images from R2
- **R2 Bucket:** `portfolio-images` ‚Äî stores image files and a `_manifest.json` for ordering/metadata
- **Site integration:** `GalleryGrid.astro` fetches images client-side from the Worker API (configured via `PUBLIC_PORTFOLIO_API_URL` env var on Cloudflare Pages)

## Contact Form Flow

1. Cloudflare Turnstile generates a token on the client
2. Form submits to the Worker at `https://paisley-contact-worker.paisley.workers.dev`
3. Worker verifies the token against Cloudflare SiteVerify API
4. Worker sends the form submission to `hello@paisleys.work` via Resend API
5. Worker sends a confirmation email to the submitter

## Worker Secrets (set via `wrangler secret put`, never in code)

**Contact Worker** (`worker/`):
- `TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY` ‚Äî Cloudflare Turnstile secret key
- `RESEND_API_KEY` ‚Äî Resend email API key

**Portfolio Worker** (`worker/portfolio/`):
- `ADMIN_PASSWORD` ‚Äî password for the admin panel

## Deploying

- **Site changes:** Push to `main` ‚Äî Cloudflare Pages builds and deploys automatically (set `PUBLIC_PORTFOLIO_API_URL` env var to the portfolio Worker URL in Cloudflare Pages settings)
- **Contact Worker changes:** Run `wrangler deploy` from the `worker/` directory
- **Portfolio Worker changes:** Run `wrangler deploy` from the `worker/portfolio/` directory
- Both Workers require `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN` env var or `wrangler login`
- The portfolio Worker requires an R2 bucket named `portfolio-images` (create via `wrangler r2 bucket create portfolio-images`)

## Key Files

- `src/pages/contact.astro` ‚Äî Contact form with Turnstile widget
- `src/components/GalleryGrid.astro` ‚Äî Portfolio gallery (fetches from portfolio API at runtime)
- `src/components/Lightbox.astro` ‚Äî Fullscreen image viewer
- `worker/index.js` ‚Äî Contact form Worker (Turnstile verification + email delivery)
- `worker/wrangler.toml` ‚Äî Contact Worker deployment config
- `worker/portfolio/index.js` ‚Äî Portfolio API Worker (R2 image management + admin UI)
- `worker/portfolio/wrangler.toml` ‚Äî Portfolio Worker deployment config
- `astro.config.mjs` ‚Äî Astro + Tailwind + Vite config
